OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cool day with a mix of sunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers which will be heavy
OL,7,Fat times with a risk of hail and
OL,8,Fthunder. Mainly light northwesterly
OL,9,Fbreeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome late sunny spells, then
OL,12,Fclear spells overnight, with
OL,13,Foccasionally heavy showers. Touch of
OL,14,Ffrost possible in sheltered spots, but
OL,15,Fnorthwesterly winds starting to
OL,16,Ffreshen towards end of night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
