OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAnother rather cold day with
OL,6,Fa mix of sunny spells and showers, the
OL,7,Fshowers heavy at times. Winds turning
OL,8,Fnortherly and becoming strong at times
OL,9,Fin coastal parts.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FSunny
OL,12,Fspells Friday with showers and
OL,13,Fnortherly winds easing. Mainly dry
OL,14,FSaturday with spells of sunshine and
OL,15,Flight winds. Dry start Sunday but
OL,16,Foutbreaks of rain edging eats in
OL,17,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
